#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:150
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我们必须明智地使用这团火焰。先把它收起来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:152
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"没错，你想起了那位披甲女士的警告——火焰的力量是有限的……你并不打算这么快就动用"
"它。当你将火焰收起时，外界那无边无际的灵魂瘟疫聚合体似乎有所反应。一部分物质"
"骤然翻腾，狂怒咆哮着朝你的飞船扑来，你脑海中的声音也在尖啸……看来它们知道自己"
"的诡计已经败露，正联合周遭的聚合体一同发动攻击！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:158
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDCOREMASS\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:174
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "你向着核心物质深处不断深入，唯有希望，为你照亮前路……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:175
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "这里的深渊也在扭曲翻腾，带着同样贪得无厌的吞噬欲。若非你的意志早已如钢铁般坚"
"定，仅仅是目睹这景象就足以让人疯狂……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:176
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "再一次跃迁——再一次深入这巨兽的腹中，这场疯狂依旧看不到尽头……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:177
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "邪恶的阴影在你视野的角落舞动，引诱你陷入偏执。你必须对这些心智诡计紧闭心扉，"
"专注于眼前的任务……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:178
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[5]"
msgstr "立于悬崖边缘摇摇欲坠，却仍要纵身向前越界——这究竟是英雄气概，还是愚莽之举，唯"
"有时间能给出答案……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"当核心聚合体再次向你展现出无边无际的体量时，你内心深处渴望着回归往昔那些简单"
"纯粹的时光。就让这份对简朴岁月的向往，化为你的动力与力量，支撑你在前方的混沌"
"之中继续深入……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:180
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_DDCOREMASS_VENTUREDEEPER\"]/text[7]"
msgstr "在这该死的地方，你一刻也不能放松警惕，否则你和你的船员就会沦为它的诡计或暴行"
"的牺牲品……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddcoremass.xml:181
